name: Playmobil Large Zoo
description:
You don’t have to drive to the zoo to see the animals and watch the caretakers feed them. This playset includes several animals that your kids surely love. They will be fascinated with the details of the miniatures that they wouldn’t want the day to end. Playing with this set and controlling the feeding times is indeed a great opportunity for every kid.

Recommended Ages: 4+

name: Sock Monkey
description:
Hang out with this special Schylling designed sock monkey, which is classic, retro and cool. It is the traditional brown, with red lips and a cute hat. It measures 20" tall.

This toy has to bring back memories. This brand new version of an old favorite is sure to be a winner. Careful- The silly Sock Monkey inside is certain to create many giggles and smiles for many years to come. Great gift for any child. Recommended for children 2 years and older. Polyester fibers. Measures approx. 20" tall. 

Recommended Ages: 2+

name: Latches Board
description:
This beautifully-crafted board has polished brass locks, latches and clasps. Brightly colored, smooth-sanded pieces help build early shape, color and size differentiation skills. Hide-and-seek pictures behind each door help develop fine motor skills. Incredible value and superior craftsmanship.

Recommended Ages: 3+

name: Farm/Zoo Train Set
description:
Fun is full steam ahead with this Zoo Animal Train Set from Melissa & Doug!

The set includes one engine, two animals, two animal cars, and eight pieces of track!

Recommended Ages: 3+

name: Special Occasion Cake
description:
Your little host will be proud to present these three layers of “delicious” yumminess. This fabulous cake from Meliissa & Doug can be topped with a bride and groom for a formal pretend wedding or with a flower bouquet to celebrate any special event. Serving and assembling this confection is easy with all the wooden layers, a selection of toppings, a server and decorative cake plate included in the “bakery” box. 

Recommended Ages: 3+
